dc_description_s: 2 maps ; 65 x 93 cm|Shows geographical locations of sperm and right whales.|"Series F."|The whale chart was released as series F a part of Maury's "Wind and current charts", series A-F. For complete discussion, see "The wind and current chart series produced by Matthew Fontaine Maury," by Marc I. Pinsel, in Navigation : Journal of the Institute of Navigation, v. 28, no. 2 (Summer, 1981), p. 123-137.|Includes text, "Diagram for Explanation," table, and note.
